QUOTE ME: OC HIGH / STUDENT NEWS & VIEWS; OC HIGH ASKS: DO SEX EDUCATION 
COURSES IN SCHOOL COVER WHAT YOU NEED TO KNOW? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Responses gathered by Amanda Garcia, El Modena; Tricia Michels, Fountain 
Valley; Koreen Kalie, Westminster; Luke Fenchel, University; Lisa Okikawa, 
Cypress; Jennifer Tobkin, Villa Park; Alison Koodrich, Ocean View; Courtney 
Adams, Corona del Mar; Julie Kim, Aliso Niguel; Tina Toochinda, Dana Hills; 
Robert Wenzel, Irvine; Judy Tsai, Huntington Beach; Tori Clive, Cypress 
