just tell you to use protection." 
</P>
<P>
 Marisa Alaniz, 16 
</P>
<P>
 junior, El Modena  
</P>
<P>
 "Sex education is the same every year. I don't need to hear what a condom is 
five times. . . . In one sentence I can sum up my feelings: Tell me something I 
don't know." 
</P>
<P>
 Mark Pearce, 17 
</P>
<P>
 junior, Aliso Niguel 
</P>
<P>
