</P>
<P>
 junior, Ocean View 
</P>
<P>
 "I think sex education in our school is limited in what they can teach us 
because of the parents' concerns of what their child can hear and learn about 
sex. I believe we have the right to know about sex and AIDS . . . to educate us 
in the future so we can live safer and happier lives." 
</P>
<P>
 San Kashani, 17 
</P>
<P>
 senior, Corona del Mar 
</P>
<P>
 "Dana Hills provides the basic knowledge that the students need to know. But 
