<DOCNO> LA012794-0054 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 007465 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 27, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 3; Column 1; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
