<DOCNO> LA012794-0197 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 007608 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 27, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
