 * Red Cross Service Centers 
</P>
<P>
 These Red Cross service centers opened Tuesday. Caseworkers can assess 
disaster-caused needs and provide vouchers for food, clothing, temporary 
housing/rental assistance, help with health/medical needs, urgent household 
items such as bedding or cookware, and some home repairs. Those who cannot be 
seen the same day will be given appointments and asked to return during the 
next day or two. Hours are 9 a.m. to 7 p.m. until further notice. 
