<HEADLINE>
<P>
SCARY BUT FUN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I was sleeping over at Lorna's house when all of a sudden there was a big 
rumbling sound that woke me up.At first I thought it was Lorna trying to wake 
me up but it did not stop. 
</P>
<P>
 Then I was convinced that it was a real earthquake. It was kind of scary and 
kind of fun. The scary part was that things were falling down. But the fun part 
about it was that me and Lorna were jumping up and down without jumping. 
</P>
<P>
 RUTH E. CHEADLE 
