FRENCH MARKET'S ROOF COLLAPSES; 3 KILLED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The concrete roof of a busy supermarket in Nice collapsed 
Wednesday.Authorities said at least three people were killed, more than 94 were 
injured and five to 10 remained trapped in the rubble. 
</P>
<P>
 Rescue crews, assisted by dogs, searched carefully into the night, working 
around chunks of concrete that had fallen into the aisles of groceries. 
</P>
<P>
 Seventy of the injured were taken to area hospitals and 30 of them were 
admitted, including six in serious condition, officials said. 
