<P>
ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY: PACIFICARE POISED FOR ACQUISITIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 PacifiCare Health Systems Inc. of Cypress said Wednesday it had obtained a 
$130-million line of credit from Chase Manhattan Bank to buy or invest in 
health-care companies. The line of credit gives the HMO a total of $300 million 
for acquisitions. 
</P>
