DMV: EXTENDED OFFICE HOURS ARE NICE, BUT WHERE ARE THE HANDBOOKS IN ENGLISH? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 This is about the DMV article of Jan. 13, Page 6.It's commendable that DMV has 
extended hours and changed days of operation to accommodate the public, but 
they have neglected to state that there are no English versions of the handbook 
available. Unless you read Spanish or Vietnamese, you're in trouble. Not only 
