<P>
 400 Degrees of Preparation -- The oven temperature was left off the recipe for 
roast lamb with potato, onion and pepper gratin in last week's Food Section 
("One-Pot Wonders," Jan. 20). The lamb should be cooked at 400 degrees for 1 
hour and 15 minutes. 
